 <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">A simple setup was designed for a ‘time-of-flight’ measurement of the sound speed in a metal bar. The experiment requires low cost components and is very simple to understand by students. A good use of it is as a demonstration experiment.</subfield>
